Title: Salaviinanpolttajat
Actors: Eero Kilpi, Teuvo Puro, Teppo Raikas
Plot: Two local men who are making moonshine in the woods. A customer comes to them, and while sampling the product they start a game of cards, which eventually leads to a fight. While the fight is going on, the local police shows up and arrests the makers while the customer manages to escape.
